The paper discusses the use of machine learning and NLP techniques for linked data refinement, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of crowdsourcing and human computation solutions, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The topic of linked data refinement is closely related to database management (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
